Word Layout Tips

	1. Click on the cell where you are wanting to insert the Content Control field.
	2. Input a Ctrl+Shift+Space Character
	3. Then insert the Content Control from the right hand menu
	4. Then apply your formatting e.g. Align Right
 
Save the document and re-open it â€“ the formatting then sticks.
 
This overcomes one of the major pains with the Word Reporting module 
